intent.user_query: What are the top 5 best-selling products by total quantity sold in the last quarter of 2023?

phases.goal:
Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductName, SUM(sd.Quantity) AS TotalQuantitySold
FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd
JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON sd.SaleID = s.SaleID
JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON sd.ProductID = p.ProductID
WHERE s.SaleDate BETWEEN '2023-10-01' AND '2023-12-31'
GROUP BY p.ProductName
ORDER BY TotalQuantitySold DESC
QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY TotalQuantitySold DESC) <= 5;

arguments.sql:
